txt.en: 'I am concerned that a number of Easterlings still occupy Lang Rhuven. If you venture into the encampment with your allies, defeat all who cross your path.'
Candúr is concerned with the number of Easterlings still occupying Lang Rhuven.
Many foes can be found in Lang Rhuven on the border of Dagorlad.\n\nYou should defeat the enemies in Lang Rhuven.
'Admirable, [placeholder]! Your deeds have earned my awe - and my thanks.'
You should return to Candúr, who can be found at a small Ranger outpost hidden in the Slag-hills.
